<records><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V01</verse_id><versetext>धृतराष्ट्र उवाच —
धर्मक्षेत्रे कुरुक्षेत्रे समवेता युयुत्सवः । 
मामकाः पाण्डवाश्चैव किमकुर्वत सञ्जय ॥ १ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V02</verse_id><versetext>सञ्जय उवाच —
दृष्ट्वा तु पाण्डवानीकं व्यूढं दुर्योधनस्तदा । 
आचार्यमुपसङ्गम्य राजा वचनमब्रवीत् ॥ २ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V03</verse_id><versetext>पश्यै तां पाण्डुपुत्राणामाचार्य महतीं चमूम् । 
व्यूढां द्रुपदपुत्रेण तव शिष्येण धीमता ॥ ३ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V04</verse_id><versetext>अत्र शूरा महेष्वासा भीमार्जुनसमा युधि । 
युयुधानो विराटश्च द्रुपदश्च महारथः ॥ ४ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V05</verse_id><versetext>धृष्टकेतुश्चेकितानः काशीराजश्च वीर्यवान् । 
पुरुजित्कुन्तिभोजश्च शैब्यश्च नरपुङ्गवः ॥ ५ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V06</verse_id><versetext>युधामन्युश्च विक्रान्त उत्तमौजाश्च वीर्यवान् । 
सौभद्रो द्रौपदेयाश्च सर्व एव महारथाः ॥ ६ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V07</verse_id><versetext>अस्माकं तु विशिष्टा ये तान्निबोध द्विजोत्तम । 
नायका मम सैन्यस्य संज्ञार्थं तान्ब्रवीमि ते ॥ ७ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V08</verse_id><versetext>भवान् भीष्मश्च कर्णश्च कृपश्च समितिञ्जयः । 
अश्वत्थामा विकर्णश्च सौमदत्तिर्जयद्रथः ॥ ८ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V09</verse_id><versetext>अन्ये च बहवः शूरा मदर्थे त्यक्तजीविताः । 
नाना शस्त्रप्रहरणाः सर्वे युद्धविशारदाः ॥ ९ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V10</verse_id><versetext>अपर्याप्तं तदस्माकं बलं भीष्माभिरक्षितम् । 
पर्याप्तं त्विदमेतेषां बलं भीमाभिरक्षितम् ॥ १० ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V11</verse_id><versetext>अयनेषु च सर्वेषु यथाभागमवस्थिताः । 
भीष्ममेवाभिरक्षन्तु भवन्तः सर्व एव हि ॥ ११ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V12</verse_id><versetext>तस्य सञ्जनयन्हर्षं कुरुवृद्धः पितामहः । 
सिंहनादं विनद्योच्चैः शङ्खं दध्मौ प्रतापवान् ॥ १२ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V13</verse_id><versetext>ततः शङ्खाश्च भेर्यश्च पणवानकगोमुखाः । 
सहसैवाभ्यहन्यन्त स शब्दस्तुमुलोऽभवत् ॥ १३ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V14</verse_id><versetext>ततः श्वेतैर्हयै र्युक्ते महति स्यन्दने स्थितौ । 
माधवः पाण्डवश्चैव दिव्यौ शङ्खौ प्रदध्मतुः ॥ १४ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V15</verse_id><versetext>पाञ्चजन्यं हृषीकेशो देवदत्तं धनञ्जयः । 
पौण्ड्रं दध्मौ महाशङ्खं भीमकर्मा वृकोदरः ॥ १५ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V16</verse_id><versetext>अनन्त विजयं राजा कुन्तीपुत्रो युधिष्ठिरः । 
नकुलः सहदेवश्च सुघोषमणिपुष्पकौ ॥ १६ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V17</verse_id><versetext>काश्यश्च परमेष्वासः शिखण्डी च महारथः । 
धृष्टद्युम्नो विराटश्च सात्यकिश्चापराजितः ॥ १७ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V18</verse_id><versetext>द्रुपदो द्रौपदेयाश्च सर्वशः पृथिवीपते । 
सौभद्रश्च महाबाहुः शङ्खान्दध्मुः पृथक्पृथक् ॥ १८ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V19</verse_id><versetext>स घोषो धार्तराष्ट्राणां हृदयानि व्यदारयत् । 
नभश्च पृथिवीं चैव तुमुलो व्यनुनादयन् ॥ १९ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V20</verse_id><versetext>अथ व्यवस्थितान्दृष्ट्वा धार्तराष्ट्रान्कपिध्वजः । 
प्रवृत्ते शस्त्रसम्पाते धनु रुद्यम्य पाण्डवः ॥ २० ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V21</verse_id><versetext>हृषीकेशं तदा वाक्यमिद माह महीपते । 
अर्जुन उवाच — 
सेनयो रुभयोर्मध्ये रथं स्थापय मेऽच्युत ॥ २१ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V22</verse_id><versetext>यावदे तान्निरीक्षेऽहं योद्धुकामानवस्थितान् । 
कैर्मया सह योद्धव्यमस्मिन्रणसमुद्यमे ॥ २२ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V23</verse_id><versetext>योत्स्यमाना नवेक्षेऽहं य एतेऽत्र समागताः । 
धार्तराष्ट्रस्य दुर्बुद्धेर्युद्धे प्रियचिकीर्षवः ॥ २३ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V24</verse_id><versetext>सञ्जय उवाच —
एव मुक्तो हृषीकेशो गुडाकेशेन भारत । 
सेनयोरुभयोर्मध्ये स्थापयित्वा रथोत्तमम् ॥ २४ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V25</verse_id><versetext>भीष्मद्रोणप्रमुखतः सर्वेषां च महीक्षिताम् । 
उवाच पार्थ पश्यैतान्समवेतान्कुरूनिति ॥ २५ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V26</verse_id><versetext>तत्रा पश्यत्स्थितान्पार्थः पितॄनथ पितामहान् । 
आचार्यान्मातुलान्भ्रातॄन्पुत्रान्पौत्रान्सखींस्तथा ॥ २६ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V27</verse_id><versetext>श्वशुरान्सुहृदश्चैवसेनयोरुभयोरपि । 
ता न्समीक्ष्य स कौन्तेयः सर्वान्बन्धूनवस्थितान् ॥ २७ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V28</verse_id><versetext>कृपया परयाविष्टो विषीदन्निदमब्रवीत् । 
अर्जुन उवाच — 
दृष्ट्वे मान्स्वजनान्कृष्ण युयुत्सून्समुपस्थितान् ॥ २८ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V29</verse_id><versetext>सीदन्ति मम गात्राणि मुखं च परिशुष्यति । 
वेपथुश्च शरीरे मे रोमहर्षश्च जायते ॥ २९ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V30</verse_id><versetext>गाण्डीवं स्रंसते हस्तात्त्वक्चैव परिदह्यते । 
न च शक्नोम्यवस्थातुं भ्रमतीव च मे मनः ॥ ३० ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V31</verse_id><versetext>निमित्तानि च पश्यामि विपरीतानि केशव । 
न च श्रेयोऽनुपश्यामि हत्वा स्वजनमाहवे ॥ ३१ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V32</verse_id><versetext>न काङ्क्षे विजयं कृष्ण न च राज्यं सुखानि च । 
किं नो राज्येन गोविन्द किं भोगैर्जीवितेन वा ॥ ३२ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V33</verse_id><versetext>येषा मर्थे काङ्क्षितं नो राज्यं भोगाः सुखानि च । 
त इमेऽवस्थिता युद्धे प्राणांस्त्यक्त्वा धनानि च ॥ ३३ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V34</verse_id><versetext>आचार्याः पितरः पुत्रास्तथैव च पितामहाः । 
मातुलाः श्वशुराः पौत्राः स्यालाः सम्बन्धिनस्तथा ॥ ३४ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V35</verse_id><versetext>एता न्न हन्तुमिच्छामि घ्नतोऽपि मधुसूदन । 
अपि त्रैलोक्यराज्यस्य हेतोः किं नु महीकृते ॥ ३५ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V36</verse_id><versetext>निहत्य धार्तराष्ट्रान्नः का प्रीतिः स्याज्जनार्दन । 
पापमेवा श्रयेदस्मान्हत्वैतानाततायिनः ॥ ३६ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V37</verse_id><versetext>तस्मा न्नार्हा वयं हन्तुं धार्तराष्ट्रान्सबान्धवान् । 
स्वजनं हि कथं हत्वा सुखिनः स्याम माधव ॥ ३७ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V38</verse_id><versetext>यद्य प्येते न पश्यन्ति लोभोपहतचेतसः । 
कुलक्षयकृतं दोषं मित्रद्रोहे च पातकम् ॥ ३८ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V39</verse_id><versetext>कथं न ज्ञेयमस्माभिः पापादस्मान्निवर्तितुम् । 
कुलक्षयकृतं दोषं प्रपश्यद्भिर्जनार्दन ॥ ३९ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V40</verse_id><versetext>कुल क्षये प्रणश्यन्ति कुलधर्माः सनातनाः । 
धर्मे नष्टे कुलं कृत्स्नमधर्मोऽभिभवत्युत ॥ ४० ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V41</verse_id><versetext>अधर्मा भिभवात्कृष्ण प्रदुष्यन्ति कुलस्त्रियः । 
स्त्रीषु दुष्टासु वार्ष्णेय जायते वर्णसङ्करः ॥ ४१ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V42</verse_id><versetext>सङ्करो नरकायैव कुलघ्नानां कुलस्य च । 
पतन्ति पितरो ह्येषां लुप्त पिण्डोदकक्रियाः ॥ ४२ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V43</verse_id><versetext>दोषै रेतैः कुलघ्नानां वर्णसङ्करकारकैः । 
उत्साद्यन्ते जातिधर्माः कुलधर्माश्च शाश्वताः ॥ ४३ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V44</verse_id><versetext>उत्सन्न कुलधर्माणां मनुष्याणां जनार्दन । 
नरके नियतं वासो भवतीत्य नुशुश्रुम ॥ ४४ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V45</verse_id><versetext>अहो बत महत्पापं कर्तुं व्यवसिता वयम् । 
यद्राज्यसुखलोभेन हन्तुं स्वजनमुद्यताः ॥ ४५ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V46</verse_id><versetext>यदि मामप्रतीकारमशस्त्रं शस्त्रपाणयः । 
धार्तराष्ट्रा रणे हन्युस्तन्मे क्षेमतरं भवेत् ॥ ४६ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record><record><source_url>https://advaitasharada.sringeri.net/display/bhashya/Gita/devanagari</source_url><source_sha256>39423dfeb0807452ffd6c4a9af1cbd863264efccf834adf712c8b5aacd822912</source_sha256><chapter_id>BG_C01</chapter_id><verse_id>BG_C01_V47</verse_id><versetext>सञ्जय उवाच —
एव मुक्त्वार्जुनः सं‍ख्ये रथोपस्थ उपाविशत् । 
विसृज्य सशरं चापं शोकसंविग्नमानसः ॥ ४७ ॥</versetext><leading_bhashya /><bhashya_blocks /><citations /></record></records>